list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add new documentation for admin panel and cloud features
This commit introduces extensive updates to the documentation, including sections on user preferences, customizing CSS, preview functionality, and Payload Cloud features. These docs aim to improve clarity and provide practical examples for developers and admins setting up or extending Payload projects.

task.summary:
Remove payload_3.wiki directory and related files
Deleted the entire `payload_3.wiki` directory, including the `.gitignore` and `README.md` files, as they are no longer needed. This cleanup helps streamline the repository and remove outdated or unused content.
